BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (WHY KIDS ARE PICKY \(It's Normal!\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Picky eating peaks between ages 2-6. It's developmental, not defiance.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (- Neophobia \(fear of new\) is a survival instinct) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (- Kids may need 15-20 exposures before accepting a new food) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (- Pressure and force ALWAYS backfire) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (- Division of responsibility: Parent decides WHAT and WHEN. Child decides IF and HOW) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (MUCH.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
