10 0 obj
<< /Length 761 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (MEALTIME RULES \(Post at the Table\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (  1. You don't have to eat it. You DO have to sit with the family.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (  2. No 'yuck' or 'gross' - you can say 'no thank you') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (  3. New foods go on the 'explorer plate' \(no pressure\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (  4. One safe food always served \(bread, rice, fruit\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (  5. Meals last 20-30 minutes, then kitchen closes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (  6. No short-order cooking \(one meal for everyone\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (  7. No screens at the table) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.0 Td (  8. Snacks are 2 hours before meals \(not right before\)) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
