BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SNEAK-IT-IN RECIPES) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (\(Use ALONGSIDE open exposure, not as a replacement for it\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 662.2 Td (1. Hidden Veggie Pasta Sauce) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (Blend: 1 can tomatoes + 1 carrot + 1 zucchini + handful spinach) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (Cook: Simmer 20 min. Kids won't see or taste the veggies!) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 604.4 Td (2. Smoothie Popsicles) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (Blend: banana + berries + yogurt + handful spinach \(turns it green-purple\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.4 Td (Pour into molds. Kids eat veggies as a 'treat'!) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 546.6 Td (3. Zucchini Muffins) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (Your favorite muffin recipe + 1 cup shredded zucchini. They dissolve!) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 502.8 Td (4. Cauliflower Mac & Cheese) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.8 Td (Steam cauliflower, blend into cheese sauce. Same taste, added nutrition.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 459.0 Td (5. Veggie Quesadillas) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 443.0 Td (Finely diced peppers + beans + cheese in tortilla. Melted cheese hides veggies!) Tj ET
endstream
