BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (FOOD EXPLORATION ACTIVITIES) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Making food FUN reduces fear. Try these with no eating pressure:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (- Food art: make faces/pictures with fruit and veggies) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (- Grow it: plant herbs or tomatoes together) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (- Shop it: let child choose ONE new food to try) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (- Cook it: kids who help cook are more likely to eat) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (- Science it: 'What happens when we cook broccoli?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (- Rate it: blind taste tests with ratings \(fun, not pressure\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.0 Td (- Build it: kebabs, wraps, pizza where THEY assemble) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 578.0 Td (- Story it: read books about food and trying new things) Tj ET
endstream
